{"tid":437642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球EMBA排名　科大港大奪冠亞","createTime":"2017-10-16T07:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T10:12:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9482e011a6ffbdd20c56f553685ea97a6ba471d","tid":437642,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171016/20184294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171016%2F20184294&d=nBD%2B0oRb4ayqU%2FApFVeel49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=83160c5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171016%2F20184294&h=93edecfb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171016/20184294</a><br />\n<br />\n全球EMBA排名　科大港大奪冠亞<br />\n<br />\n14,726<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171016/large/17990372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171016%2Flarge%2F17990372.jpg&h=c234c79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港大學與倫敦商學院及哥倫比亞商學院合辦的「EMBA-Global Asia行政人員工商管理學碩士課程」，獲得全球第二。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國《金融時報》公佈新一年全球EMBA（行政人員工商管理碩士）課程排名，預料本港兩所大學有份合辦的課程將包辦冠亞，其中香港大學首次參與即擠身第二，據悉榜首由科技大學蟬聯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畢業生平均年薪250萬至366萬<br />\n<br />\n香港大學經濟及工商管理學院表示，與倫敦商學院及哥倫比亞商學院合辦的「EMBA-Global Asia行政人員工商管理學碩士課程」，今年首次參與《金融時報》排名，即獲得全球第二。該課程的畢業生薪酬，為平均年薪將近32萬美元（約250萬港元），即月薪逾20萬港元；於國際課程經驗排第7名，而課程畢業生的事業發展表現則位列第14位。<br />\n<br />\n該學院院長蔡洪濱對位列第二感到高興及鼓舞，指課程融合香港、倫敦，以及紐約的優勢，結合了強大的校友網絡，讓課程學生掌握最新的商業知識。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，科大與美國西北大學凱洛格管理學院合辦的Kellogg-HKUST EMBA課程會蟬聯上述排行榜第一名。該課程自2013年起一直名列前茅，分別於2014、2015年排第二，2013年及去年排第一。去年數據顯示學生畢業3年後平均年薪達46.9萬美元（約366萬港元），科大今日將公佈排名詳情。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》EMBA排行榜每年選出世界前100位的EMBA課程，有17年歷史，涵蓋畢業生薪酬、就業發展、學術質素等項目計分。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n臨近光棍節　紙箱月內兩加價<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n新系統欠佳　傳消防撤3主管"},{"pid":"1d82f32e6da73c1dc5168144e0293156ffe19d2a","tid":437642,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"香港商業大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f2d2fd08cf39276941452a431426fd198abde4","tid":437642,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"ust 又有得打飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fc2c488ad364eb91d53677188522aa65cbfe16","tid":437642,"uid":132769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"臨近光棍節　紙箱月內兩加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfeb4395e2620e38c1196da7998c04d656767ab6","tid":437642,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"終於有樣野可以屌打Nus 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5fdff4dd5020b828b7f7ded7dbc6c5979aee52","tid":437642,"uid":61329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"有邊d真係有料既人讀EMBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n大集團CEO都多都係MBA"},{"pid":"d17a8ee47103cc20ddfb497c9b187d38b0ac8592","tid":437642,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死on9仔LIKLN<br />\n而家覆post俾你個冚家剷投訴<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f18jhd4s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff18jhd4s&h=196337c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fac8a6a3928c4a0e7d43c148ed089a075cdd22e5","tid":437642,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有樣野可以屌打Nus 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前除咗牙醫之外乜都俾NUS屌打<img 